parameters: There is one crystal placed in each map.

You can recover here, so please make use of it for
dungeon conquest.
There's no need to go any further.
Aeru came, ehehe, it's been a while, hasn't it?

Recently, my belly has gotten bigger so I can't go
out as much... I'm happy, but it's a little tough.

When I give birth, I plan to return to the
village, so please take care of things then.

I know! Since you're here, I'll make some food for
you! If you'd like, please eat it!

It looks like the sun is about to set, so I'll
take you up on your offer and stay the night.

Yeah, yeah! That sounds good! I'm feeling happy
for some reason.

The barrier is set up, so we can't seem to get
inside without doing something about it...

From beyond the barrier, the sound of something
colliding violently and a woman's voice can be
heard.

Came to see Lira-san? Um, maybe it's better to
stop for now...

Okusuke's condition is worsening, and, um, that's
why... it might be better to come back later.

Aeru, it's good to see you. Lira will be happy
too.

Lira-chan is cute, isn't she? I wonder if I should
also marry a human girl.
